* [[雨果·威明|雨果·威明]]饰演[[V_(漫畫人物)|V]]，一名具有獨特魅力與高超武術的自由鬥士，戴著[[盖伊·福克斯面具|盖伊·福克斯面具]]，是[[北方之火|北方之火]]為了進行活體實驗而找來的實驗體之一，計畫透過恐怖襲擊點燃革命，進而推翻當時掌權的[[極權主義|極權]]政府。
:原先飾演V一角的演員為[[詹姆斯·鮑弗|詹姆斯·鮑弗]]，但他在電影开拍后六個星期便离开了剧组，理由是他無法忍受在整部電影中都戴着面具<ref name="purefoy">{{cite web |work=Starpulse.com |title=James Purefoy Quit 'V for Vendetta' Because He Hated Wearing The Mask |url=http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2006/02/24/james_purefoy_quit_v_for_vendetta_becaus |accessdate=2006-04-07 |date=2006-02-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060924012538/http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2006/02/24/james_purefoy_quit_v_for_vendetta_becaus |archivedate=2006-09-24 }}</ref>。取而代之的是曾在[[駭客任務系列|《駭客任務》系列]]與[[乔·西佛|乔·西佛]]和[[沃卓斯基姐妹|沃卓斯基姐妹]]合作過的雨果·威明。不过，在片尾中仍可見到有幾個由詹姆斯·鮑弗飾演V的镜头，只不过[[配音|配音]]的部分依然由雨果·威明負責。<ref name="MTV">{{cite web | work=MTV | author=Vineyard, Jennifer | title=Rebels without a pause. Portman and Weaving fight the power in V for Vendetta | url=http://www.mtv.com/shared/movies/features/v/v_for_vendetta_060310/index2.jhtml?epiNum=1 | accessdate=2006-05-03 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717003507/http://www.mtv.com/shared/movies/features/v/v_for_vendetta_060310/index2.jhtml?epiNum=1 | archivedate=2015-07-17 | deadurl=no }}</ref>對於V這個角色，威明在受訪時表示，「他是個非常瀟灑、魅力十足又浪漫的人物，但他也有扭曲、受過創傷的一面。V終究只是個概念，稱不上一個真正的人」<ref name="WeavingInterview">{{cite web |last=Foley |first=Jack |url=http://www.indielondon.co.uk/Film-Review/v-for-vendetta-hugo-weaving-interview |title=V For Vendetta - Hugo Weaving interview |publisher=IndieLondon |date=2005-05-23 |accessdate=2019-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190310204656/http://www.indielondon.co.uk/Film-Review/v-for-vendetta-hugo-weaving-interview |archive-date=2019-03-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

