rd Wins and Nominations|publisher=IMDb|accessdate=2010-05-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207080936/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0434409/awards|archivedate=2016-12-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

